    "text": "Investigations have revealed that a married couple residing at Sirisara Uyana, Baseline Mawatha, Borella, had allegedly been engaged in drug trafficking activities since 2017, and that the proceeds generated from those activities had been deposited into bank accounts maintained in the name of the suspect\u2019s mother.",
    "fonts": [
