    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      777.23,
      526.17,
      818.11
    ],
    "text": "Further inquiries have disclosed that the suspect had utilised the unlawfully acquired funds to purchase a six-perch property, including a house, situated at 8th Lane, Shantha Lokagama, Korathota, Athurugiriya, Oruwala, for nearly Rs. 3 million in December 2023.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
