      72.02,
      31.91,
      526.13,
      72.79
    ],
    "text": "Accordingly, under the provisions of the Prevention of Money Laundering Act, a detention and deactivation order has been issued on the said land and house for a period of seven days with effect from 20.05.2026.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
